<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>About</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; text-indent: 40px">
            Learn more about Drexell & Honeybees, why Lisa McMillan founded it and what it means to the Brewton community.
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/Home/About">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Volunteer</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; text-indent: 40px">Make a difference in your community! Drexell & Honeybee's needs volunteers. Individuals and groups are welcome</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default"  href="/Volunteers/Create">Sign up &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Donate</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; text-indent: 40px">Making a monetary donation is one way that you can support the mission of Drexell & Honeybee's and make a difference in your community.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/Home/Donate">Donate &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
</div>